    "body": "Sure!\r\n\r\nBefore:\r\n\r\n``` html\r\n<div data-app='current-filters'>\r\n    <div class='ais-CurrentRefinements__root'>\r\n        <div class='ais-CurrentRefinements__items'>\r\n            <div class='ais-CurrentRefinements__item ais-CurrentRefinements__itemParent'><span class='ais-CurrentRefinements__itemLabel'>category: </span>\r\n                <div class='ais-CurrentRefinements__item'><span class='ais-CurrentRefinements__itemLabel'>booms</span>\r\n                    <button class='ais-CurrentRefinements__itemClear'>\r\n                        <svg fill='currentColor' preserveAspectRatio='xMidYMid meet' height='1em' width='1em' viewBox='0 0 40 40' style='vertical-align: baseline;'>\r\n                            <g>\r\n                                <path d='m31.6 10.7l-9.3 9.3 9.3 9.3-2.3 2.3-9.3-9.3-9.3 9.3-2.3-2.3 9.3-9.3-9.3-9.3 2.3-2.3 9.3 9.3 9.3-9.3z' />\r\n                            </g>\r\n                        </svg>\r\n                    </button>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class='ais-CurrentRefinements__item'><span class='ais-CurrentRefinements__itemLabel'>masts</span>\r\n                    <button class='ais-CurrentRefinements__itemClear'>\r\n                        <svg fill='currentColor' preserveAspectRatio='xMidYMid meet' height='1em' width='1em' viewBox='0 0 40 40' style='vertical-align: baseline;'>\r\n                            <g>\r\n                                <path d='m31.6 10.7l-9.3 9.3 9.3 9.3-2.3 2.3-9.3-9.3-9.3 9.3-2.3-2.3 9.3-9.3-9.3-9.3 2.3-2.3 9.3 9.3 9.3-9.3z' />\r\n                            </g>\r\n                        </svg>\r\n                    </button>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\nAfter:\r\n\r\n``` html\r\n<div class=\"ais-CurrentRefinements__root\">\r\n    <div class=\"ais-CurrentRefinements__items\">\r\n        <div class=\"ais-CurrentRefinements__item ais-CurrentRefinements__itemParent\"><span